We share the movement

42
00:01:45,810 --> 00:01:47,479
and search for truth

43
00:01:47,490 --> 00:01:49,650
Floating moon, violet

44
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:53,070
Confirmation as we magnetize

45
00:01:53,070 --> 00:01:55,660
(Tides encountered)

46
00:01:55,660 --> 00:01:58,990
And now we're standing

47
00:01:58,990 --> 00:02:00,910
Close your eyes

48
00:02:00,910 --> 00:02:04,170
Even when noise confines

49
00:02:04,170 --> 00:02:06,040
There is a guide inside

50
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:09,759
that shows what you must defy

51
