Crush them to pieces swallow

54
00:02:15,220 --> 00:02:16,550
and let it sink in

55
00:02:16,550 --> 00:02:22,310
Now a brand new chapter shall begin

56
00:02:23,890 --> 00:02:26,860
Blood's racing through my veins

57
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:30,900
There's something that I must keep safe

58
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:32,240
Though unsure

59
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:35,740
I move on with conviction

60
00:02:35,740 --> 00:02:38,660
With the tear tracks shining bright

61
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:42,400
New places we've belonged, we find

62
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:45,670
Done with counting what's missing

63
00:02:45,670 --> 00:02:50,050
Embrace what's around, we're moving on

64
00:02:50,050 --> 00:02:52,340
Bridging stories

65
